UID:uQrfVebxCdQQQ8Z-UraRx
SUMMARY:GirlBrunch
DTSTAMP:20260318T063032Z
DTSTART:20260322T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Brunch\, music\, and grown-woman energy.\n\nJoin us for a curat
	ed daytime experience featuring a live DJ\, elevated brunch selections \\(
	vegans incl.\\) and drinks!\n\nComing with your girls? Perfect.\n\nComing 
	solo and looking to meet new friends? Also perfect.\n\nGirl Brunch is desi
	gned to feel welcoming\,— whether you arrive with a group or by yourself.\
	n\nDress up. Show up. Be open.\n\nLimited tickets available.\n\nIf you hav
	e dietary needs\, note that in your purchase before checkout! Gotta make s
	ure you’re fed right girl!\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/detail
	s/girlbrunch/18162842/2026-03-22T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Arts & Culture
